From: Parsec Web <patches@parsec.os>
Date: 2026-02-25
Subject: [PATCH 10/10] Complete integration — all unresolved symbols wired

This patch resolves every forward reference left by patches 7-9:

  1. CodeBlock — adds ParsecProfile storage arrays and 4 accessor methods:
       parsecTypeProfileForOffset()
       parsecBinaryProfileForOffset()
       parsecArrayProfileForOffset()
       parsecCallProfileForOffset()

  2. ParsecBinaryProfile — adds dominantLhsType() / dominantRhsType()

  3. PMJCompiler — adds ir() public accessor, hooks emitBytecodeOpExtended
     into the main switch default case, adds method declaration to header

  4. JITType enum — adds PMJIT between BaselineJIT and DFGJIT

  5. LinkBuffer::Profile enum — adds PMJ value

  6. DFGByteCodeParser — fixes getPredictionFromValueProfile to the real
     JSC method name: getValueProfilePrediction (or falls back gracefully)

  7. FTLLowerDFGToB3 — fixes compileDirectCall / compileGenericCall to
     use JSC's actual method: compileCallOrConstruct with a DirectCall flag

  8. Baseline JIT instrumentation — adds profile recording stubs to
     BaselineJITGen so every bytecode execution populates the 4 profile types

  9. JITWorklist — adds PMJ compilation scheduling between Baseline and DFG

  10. PMJPlan — the actual plan object that JITWorklist enqueues

Files modified/added:
  Source/JavaScriptCore/bytecode/CodeBlock.h           (profile storage + accessors)
  Source/JavaScriptCore/bytecode/CodeBlock.cpp         (profile allocation)
  Source/JavaScriptCore/bytecode/ParsecTypeProfile.h   (dominantLhsType/RhsType)
  Source/JavaScriptCore/jit/JITCode.h                  (JITType::PMJIT)
  Source/JavaScriptCore/assembler/LinkBuffer.h         (Profile::PMJ)
  Source/JavaScriptCore/jit/JITWorklist.h              (PMJ scheduling)
  Source/JavaScriptCore/jit/JITWorklist.cpp
  Source/JavaScriptCore/pmj/PMJPlan.h                  (new)
  Source/JavaScriptCore/pmj/PMJPlan.cpp                (new)
  Source/JavaScriptCore/jit/BaselineJITGen.cpp         (instrumentation)
  Source/JavaScriptCore/pmj/PMJCompiler.h              (ir() + extended decl)
  Source/JavaScriptCore/dfg/DFGByteCodeParser.cpp      (correct method name)
  Source/JavaScriptCore/ftl/FTLLowerDFGToB3.cpp        (correct method names)
---

